## 四、安装机制

### 4.1 一键安装脚本

**Linux/macOS** (`install.sh`)：

```bash
#!/bin/bash
OS=$(uname -s | tr '[:upper:]' '[:lower:]')
ARCH=$(uname -m)
case $ARCH in x86_64) ARCH="amd64" ;; aarch64|arm64) ARCH="arm64" ;; esac

UPDATE_URL="${UPDATE_URL:-https://releases.example.com/mycli/version.json}"
VERSION=$(curl -fsSL "$UPDATE_URL" | jq -r '.latest')

RELEASE_BASE="${RELEASE_BASE:-https://releases.example.com/mycli}"
DOWNLOAD_URL="${RELEASE_BASE}/releases/${VERSION}/mycli-${OS}-${ARCH}"

INSTALL_DIR="${INSTALL_DIR:-$HOME/.local/bin}"
mkdir -p "$INSTALL_DIR"
curl -fsSL -o "$INSTALL_DIR/mycli" "$DOWNLOAD_URL"
chmod +x "$INSTALL_DIR/mycli"
```

**关键**：安装脚本应支持通过环境变量自定义源，便于企业内网部署。

### 4.2 安装路径

| 平台 | 安装路径 | 配置路径 |
|------|----------|----------|
| Linux/macOS | `~/.local/bin/` 或 `/usr/local/bin/` | `~/.config/mycli/` |
| Windows | `%LOCALAPPDATA%\mycli\bin\` | `%APPDATA%\mycli\` |

